办理健康证还要缴费？官方回应：不违规。
Payment for a health card? Official response: No violation.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 钟煜豪日前，针对市民反映的“医院办理健康证明要求缴费100元”一事，河南邓州市政府网站刊发了涉事的邓州市第二人民医院回应称，收取的费用为胸片、血常规等检查费，不违规。
In response to a public complaint that hospitals should pay $100 to obtain a medical certificate, the Second People's Hospital in Dunzhou, Henan Province, responded that the fee charged was a chest film, blood routine check-up and so on, according to a report published on the website of the Henan State Municipal Government.
有市民此前通过网络介绍，本人2020年2月26日在市第二人民医院办理河南省新冠肺炎健康申报证明时被该院强制做抽血、拍片项目，并且收取100元检查费。
Some people have been introduced through the Internet, I was in the Second People's Hospital of Henan Province on February 26, 2020 when the health declaration certificate for Xinguan Pneumonia was forced to do the blood, film project, and charged 100 yuan inspection fees.
河南省新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情防控指挥部发布的《关于有序做好新型冠状肺炎健康申报证明办理服务工作的通知》及南阳市新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情防控指挥部发布的《关于进一步规范新型冠状肺炎疫情防控期间居民健康证明办理的补充通知》，明确规定在健康证明办理过程中不得收取费用，不得变相或者搭车检查。
The Notice Concerning the Work of Serving the New Coronavirus Pneumonia Declaration and Services Issued by the Henan New Coronavirus Pneumonia Control Command and the Supplementary Notice Concerning the Handling of Health Certificates During the Prevention and Control of the New Coronavirus Pneumonia in Nanyang City, clearly stipulates that no fees shall be charged during the processing of the health certificate and no disguised or voluntary inspection shall be allowed.
请问此项检查费收取是否合理？如不合理如何退款？就此问题，邓州市第二人民医院介绍，邓州市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作指挥部办公室《关于进一步加强对商超、宾馆人群密集场所复工、开工疫情防控工作的紧急通知》明确规定，对以上人员进行胸片、血常规、C反应蛋白的体检，三项检查项目费用总计为110元/人次，但根据文件要求我们对每人收费为100元。
Is the inspection fee reasonable? If it is not reasonable how to refund? On this issue, Deng Zhou Second People's Hospital said that the "Emergency Notice on Further Strengthening the Work to Prevent and Control the New Coronavirus Infection in Dunzhou City" clearly stipulates that the above-mentioned persons should be given a medical check-up on sternum, blood routine and C-reactive protein.
不属于违规收费。
No fee is charged for violations.
对于网民举报的无法通过医保卡缴费并开具发票问题，医院称，根据职工医保的政策要求，个人体检费用属于自费项目，医保刷卡系统不支持。
Netizens reported the problem of unable to pay through medical insurance card and invoice, the hospital said that according to the policy of employee health insurance, the cost of individual medical examination is a self-pay item, not supported by the medical insurance credit card system.
对于网民举报医院收费不透明、违规敛财等问题，邓州市第二人民医院认为，我们的所有健康服务工作都按照相关规定和要求进行，不存在违规收费，更不存在违规敛财。
To the netizen reports the hospital charge opaque, the violation accumulates money and so on question, the Dunzhou second people's hospital thinks, our all health service work according to the relevant regulation and the request, does not exist the illegal fee, not to mention the irregular accumulation of wealth.
“可能我院在服务过程中没有向服务对象做好解释说明，下一步我院立即改正，并就此事向网民致以歉意。
"Maybe the hospital did not do a good job of explaining to the clients in the service process. The next step is to rectify the situation immediately and apologize to the netizens.
